PN,44901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA man who stole Noah Donohoe's missing
OL,8,Flaptop has denied that it is his hand
OL,9,Fin a picture discovered on the
OL,10,Fschoolboy's phone after he was last
OL,11,Fseen.
OL,13,FDaryl Paul told Belfast Coroner's
OL,14,FCourt that he had "never set eyes" on
OL,15,FNoah and insisted under questioning
OL,16,Fthat he had never been in possession
OL,17,Fof his green coat or phone.
OL,19,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,20,Fschoolboy, which is being heard before
OL,21,Fa jury, is now in its 13th week.
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,8,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,9,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,10,FBelfast on June 27 2020, six days
OL,11,Fafter leaving home on his bike to meet
OL,12,Ftwo friends in the Cavehill area of
OL,13,Fthe city.
OL,15,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,16,Flikely cause of death was drowning.
OL,18,FNoah's mother Fiona Donohoe has
OL,19,Fattended every day of the long-running
OL,20,Fproceedings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPaul, of Cliftonville Avenue,
OL,8,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to stealing
OL,9,Fa rucksack containing Noah's laptop
OL,10,Fand books.
OL,12,FHe resumed giving evidence on Monday
OL,13,Fwhen he was questioned by Brenda
OL,14,FCampbell KC, who represents Ms Donohoe.
OL,16,FPointing out that Paul had previously
OL,17,Flied under police questioning, the
OL,18,Fbarrister said there were aspects of
OL,19,Fhis possession of Noah's belongings
OL,20,Fthat "call for questions to be asked".
OL,26,@|D@FOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe jury was shown CCTV footage of
OL,8,FPaul in the Queen's Quarter area of
OL,9,FBelfast, close to Noah's Fitzroy
OL,10,FAvenue home, from the evening the
OL,11,Fschoolboy disappeared.
OL,13,FPaul said he had been in the area to
OL,14,Fsee Maria Nolan, who he said he had
OL,15,Frecently met, and who has previously
OL,16,Fgiven evidence at the inquest.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Campbell said: "On those occasions
OL,8,Fwhen you hung outside Queen's Quarter
OL,9,Flike this afternoon, do you think you
OL,10,Fwould have seen Noah? Did you speak to
OL,11,Fhim?"
OL,13,FPaul replied: "No, never."
OL,15,FShe asked him if he had any knowledge
OL,16,Fof Noah leaving his home for a short
OL,17,Fperiod on the night before he
OL,18,Fdisappeared.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@EO]uD@OOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPaul said: "I don't know a single
OL,8,Fthing and if I did I would be the
OL,9,Ffirst to tell you, I have a heart."
OL,11,FThe jury was then shown CCTV footage
OL,12,Fof Noah cycling past Paul in Queen's
OL,13,FQuarter, wearing his green coat and
OL,14,Fcarrying his rucksack.
OL,16,FMs Campbell said: "This is the last
OL,17,Ftime he leaves home, and you're within
OL,18,Fa matter of metres of him."
OL,26,@oD@LOUqD@cO]xD@SOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe pointed out that within an hour,
OL,8,FNoah's rucksack ended up in a green
OL,9,Fbag Paul is seen carrying in the
OL,10,Ffootage.
OL,12,FThe witness said: "I have no knowledge
OL,13,Fof that wee boy passing me."
OL,15,FThe barrister said: "What I want to
OL,16,Fexplore on behalf of Noah's mother is
OL,17,Fthis series of coincidences, to
OL,18,Funderstand whether they are
OL,19,Fcoincidences or whether there's reason
OL,20,Fto be more concerned."
OL,26,@tD@SOUuD@\O]wD@UOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Campbell continued: "Did you look
OL,8,Fin the direction of Noah after he went
OL,9,Fpast?"
OL,11,FPaul responded: "I did. Just a natural
OL,12,Fthing, I guess."
OL,14,FMs Campbell said Paul had then
OL,15,Ftravelled towards Royal Avenue in
OL,16,FBelfast city centre while showing the
OL,17,Fjury a map of the route Noah cycled
OL,18,Fthrough the city.
OL,20,FPaul said: "I was only on same path as
OL,21,FNoah for a short distance."
OL,26,@oD@XOUqD@FO]sD@QOUtD@PO]|D@LOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe barrister said Paul had claimed
OL,8,Fduring an interview with a journalist
OL,9,Fthat he had found Noah's rucksack
OL,10,Fcontaining his laptop on the ground in
OL,11,Fa covered walkway in the York Street/
OL,12,FFrederick Street area.
OL,14,FThe jury was shown footage of Noah
OL,15,Fcycling past that area without
OL,16,Fstopping.
OL,18,FMs Campbell said: "I am going to
OL,19,Fsuggest where you told the journalist
OL,20,Fthat you found Noah's bag is not where
OL,21,Fit was... you are wrong about that."
OL,26,@zD@SOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPaul said: "I can only tell you where
OL,8,FI found it. If I lied about that, what
OL,9,Fsignificance would that lie hold?"
OL,11,FMs Campbell said: "Until this point in
OL,12,Ftime we have got the coincidence of
OL,13,Fyou being outside Queen's Quarter and
OL,14,Fnow the coincidence of you being on
OL,15,Fthat part of his journey.
OL,17,F"But the coincidences, I am going to
OL,18,Fsuggest, don't stop there."
OL,26,@oD@LOUqD@bO]sD@SOUyD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe barrister said the jury had
OL,8,Fpreviously heard evidence about an
OL,9,Fanonymous caller to police who stated
OL,10,FPaul had been in possession of Noah's
OL,11,Fgreen coat.
OL,13,FPaul said: "I was not in possession of
OL,14,Fany green coat."
OL,16,FShe said: "It would be another
OL,17,Fcoincidence upon coincidence?"
OL,19,FHe said: "I did not have his coat."
OL,26,@uD@LOUvD@PO]xD@KOUyD@^O]{D@JOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe barrister asked the witness if he
OL,8,Fhad next "followed Noah's journey"
OL,9,Ffrom the city centre along North Queen
OL,10,FStreet.
OL,12,FHe said he had not.
OL,14,FShe continued: "To the location where
OL,15,Fthe phone was found?"
OL,17,FPaul said: "No."
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@bO]vD@POUwD@UO]yD@LOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Campbell said: "Do you know
OL,8,Fanything about Noah's phone? Did you
OL,9,Fhave it in your hand? Did you find it
OL,10,Fin his coat pocket or in his rucksack?
OL,12,FHe answered: "No."
OL,14,FThe barrister said a report from a
OL,15,Fpolice expert had revealed a
OL,16,Fphotograph of a hand on Noah's phone
OL,17,Ftaken on the evening he disappeared,
OL,18,F40 minutes after he was last seen.
OL,20,FShe said: "Is that your hand?"
OL,26,@oD@SOUtD@NOUtD@RO]|D@KOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPaul responded: "No, it is not my
OL,8,Fhand."
OL,10,FThe barrister said police arrested
OL,11,FPaul later on the same day but he was
OL,12,Fnever asked where he had found the
OL,13,Flaptop or about the green coat.
OL,15,FShe then showed the jury phone records
OL,16,Ffrom Noah's phone on the day he
OL,17,Fdisappeared.
OL,19,FMs Campbell said Noah's mother Fiona
OL,20,Fhad called her son's mobile six times
OL,21,Fon the evening he went missing.
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe said: "Whoever had Noah's phone in
OL,8,Ftheir hand at 18.50 would have a phone
OL,9,Fwith six missed calls from 'Mum'."
OL,11,FThe jury was then shown a map of the
OL,12,Farea in north Belfast where the phone
OL,13,Fwas when Ms Donohoe sent a text
OL,14,Fmessage to her son on June 21 2020.
OL,16,FShe said Victoria Parade, where Paul
OL,17,Fsaid he had gone after leaving
OL,18,FFrederick Street, was within the area
OL,19,Fof the map.
OL,21,FShe said: "Did you have Noah's phone?"
OL,26,@oD@KOUqD@bO]}D@KOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPaul said: "No, I did not."
OL,9,FMs Campbell continued: "Did you see
OL,10,Fthat message coming in and those phone
OL,11,Fcalls?"
OL,13,FHe said: "I don't appreciate that
OL,14,Fquestion, but the answer is no."
OL,16,FShe said: "It is not too late to tell
OL,17,Fthe truth, not too late to give him
OL,18,Fsome justice."
OL,20,FHe responded: "Thank you, but no."
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@[O]qD@XOUsD@GO]uD@JOUvD@`O]xD@
OL,26,AKOUzD@NO]|D@OOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777395954
OL,3,CMan who stole Noah Donohoe's laptop
OL,4,C'never set eyes' on teenager, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Campbell added: "Was it you who
OL,8,Fwent along North Queen Street and who
OL,9,Fchucked his phone over the railings
OL,10,Finto Castleton Park?"
OL,12,FHe said: "I wasn't even there."
OL,14,FShe said: "You realised this was a
OL,15,Fphone that was a bit hot, there was a
OL,16,Fmummy desperate to find her child?"
OL,18,FPaul said: "No."
OL,20,FThe inquest continues.
OL,26,@oD@TOUrD@UO]tD@JOUtD@_O]vD@KOUxD@cO]zD@
OL,26,ALOUzD@PO]
